<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm10811088">
<term>alfaeind (α-eind) (e. alpha particle (α particle))</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm10811088-meaning">jákvætt hlaðin eind sem
samanstendur af tveimur róteindum og tveimur nifteindum</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp27115648">
<term>rafeind (e. electron)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp27115648-meaning">neikvætt hlaðin öreind
með tiltölulega lítinn massa sem er staðsett fyrir utan kjarnann</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm25241664">
<term>samsætur (e. isotopes)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm25241664-meaning">atóm sem innihalda sama
fjölda róteinda en mismunandi fjölda nifteinda</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp100350096">
<term>nifteind (e. neutron)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp100350096-meaning">óhlaðin öreind staðsett
í kjarnanum</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp130134704">
<term>kjarni (e. nucleus)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp130134704-meaning">massamikil, jákvætt
hlaðin miðja atóms sem samanstendur af róteindum og nifteindum</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp21637408">
<term>róteind (e. proton)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp21637408-meaning">jákvætt hlaðin öreind
staðsett í kjarnanum</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
